# Compte Google
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User USER@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg -q -d ~/.authinfo.gpg | awk '/imap.gmail/ {print $6; exit}'"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

# Dossier IMAP par défaut (boîte de réception)
IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/.Mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.Mail/gmail/Inbox

Channel gmail
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

